    const keys=[null,'C','C#','Db','D','D#','Eb','E','F','F#','Gb','G','G#','Ab','A','A#','Bb','B','Cm','C#m','Dbm','Dm','D#m','Ebm','Em','Fm','F#m','Gbm','Gm','G#m','Abm','Am','A#m','Bbm','Bm'];if(!keys.includes(value.projectDefaults.key))value.projectDefaults.key=null;
